ichen Kinder hatte, sollten seine Nichten und Neffen sein gesamtes Haus erben.\",","    \"kapitel\": 7","  },","  {","    \"id\": 544,","    \"deutsch\": \"erpressen\",","    \"turkisch\": \"şantaj yapmak\",","    \"armenisch\": \"շանտաժի ենթարկել\",","    \"chinesisch\": \"敲诈\",","    \"farsi\": \"اخاذی کردن\",","    \"kurdisch\": \"şantaj kirin\",","    \"ukrainisch\": \"вимагати\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Die Hacker versuchten, die Bank mit den gestohlenen Kundendaten massiv zu erpressen.\",","    \"kapitel\": 7","  },","  {","    \"id\": 545,","    \"deutsch\": \"fassen\",","    \"turkisch\": \"yakalamak\",","    \"armenisch\": \"բռնել\",","    \"chinesisch\": \"抓住\",","    \"farsi\": \"دستگیر کردن\",","    \"kurdisch\": \"girtin\",","    \"ukrainisch\": \"затримувати\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Der Polizei gelang es schließlich, den flüchtigen Bankräuber in einem Versteck zu fassen.\",","    \"kapitel\": 7","  },","  {","    \"id\": 546,","    \"deutsch\": \"festnehmen, nimmt fest, nahm fest, hat festgenommen\",","    \"turkisch\": \"tutuklamak\",","    \"armenisch\": \"ձերբակալել\",","    \"chinesisch\": \"逮捕\",","    \"farsi\": \"بازداشت کردن\",","    \"kurdisch\": \"girtin\",","    \"ukrainisch\": \"заарештовувати\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Spezialeinheiten konnten den gefährlichen Terrorverdächtigen am frühen Morgen festnehmen.\",","    \"kapitel\": 7","  },","  {","    \"id\": 547,","    \"deutsch\": \"flüchten\",","    \"turkisch\": \"kaçmak\",","    \"armenisch\": \"փախչել\",","    \"chinesisch\": \"逃跑\",","    \"farsi\": \"فرار کردن\",","    \"kurdisch\": \"revîn\",","    \"ukrainisch\": \"тікати\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Nach dem missglückten Überfall versuchten die Komplizen mit einem Motorrad zu flüchten.\",","    \"kapitel\": 7","  },","  {","    \"id\": 548,","    \"deutsch\": \"lügen, lügt, log, hat gelogen\",","    \"turkisch\": \"yalan söylemek\",","    \"armenisch\": \"ստել\",","    \"chinesisch\": \"说谎\",","    \"farsi\": \"دروغ گفتن\",","    \"kurdis